PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Jeremy Loren JAMISON, Defendant-Appellant. People of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Clifford Lorenzo Johnson, Defendant-Appellant. People of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Lorenzo Warren Jamison, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157988
SC: 157989, SC: 157990
COA: 336124, COA: 336143, COA: 336154 Supreme Court of Michigan. January 16, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the April 26, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
